  "texts": [
    "Figure 3 depicts the social media posts and hashtags two participants created for London and Brussels. 1 3",
    "Education and Information Technologies (2024) 29:19343-19366 Similar to the activity presented in Fig. 3, the students also used the tool to generate answers for questions related to target vocabulary to discuss with peers in breakout rooms.",
    "Similarly, as a wrap-up activity, the students worked in groups of two on a ChatGPT-assisted creative writing exercise.",
    "Each student in the group was given a prompt by the teacher, which they pasted into the ChatGPT to brainstorm, plan, and write a story.",
    "The students took notes on the story provided by ChatGPT and shared their stories with their partners in the breakout rooms in the online class."
  ]
